{"tid":1982522,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡推「反利物浦俠」防疫捱轟","createTime":"2020-04-21T09:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T03:23:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9e931808e11a30b56ad14c2c880e761ce147ea","tid":1982522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:06:12.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】新加坡創作出5名超級英雄教育市民防疫知識，其中一個為關於利物浦的永遠獨行俠，結果大受批評，更不得不把這活動暫停。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡近日爆發新型冠狀病毒疫情，確診個案急速增長，已經超過1400宗。政府跟當地藝術團體Band of Doodlers合作，周日推出了5個超級英雄The Virus Vanguard，希望吸引大眾注意力，教育市民防疫知識。<br />\n<br />\n當中有一個叫永遠獨行俠（MAWA Man），MAWA意思是Must Always Walk Alone，強調每個人都需要保持社交距離。官方更詳細描繪了永遠獨行俠的背景，「他是成長於1980年代的曼聯球迷，當利物浦一直贏冠軍時，不停被2名利迷兄弟嘲弄，令他討厭紅軍所有事，包括你永遠不會獨行（You&rsquo;ll Never Walk Alone）的精神。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，這5個超級英雄推出僅一天，立即引來大量負評，永遠獨行俠更是受盡炮轟，政府不得不把5人暫時「革職」，「The Virus Vanguard正在被審查。如果冒犯了任何人，我們很抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Facebook圖片"},{"pid":"b734034aefca0e27c4f19db17e127bc3c05ed69d","tid":1982522,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/245/29215496245/29227092209_600x392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F245%2F29215496245%2F29227092209_600x392.jpg&h=534d6473&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db514f9de768c1ed690e98a73df1feb0fd21085d","tid":1982522,"uid":48631,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"Monkey迫害我利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf0b78ae4e4e886bc31387567ac5fc448634a08","tid":1982522,"uid":11694,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"弱智marketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\